graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|pipeline execution| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+<br/>REQUIRED]
    DSPO -->|platform services| OCP[OpenShift Container Platform<br/>4.9+<br/>REQUIRED]
    DSPO -->|upstream project| KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>1.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    DSPO -->|tekton adapter| KFPTekton[kfp-tekton<br/>1.5.x<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Conditional)
    DSPO -.->|external DB| ExtDB[MySQL-compatible Database<br/>CONDITIONAL<br/>if not using MariaDB]
    DSPO -.->|external storage| ExtS3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>CONDITIONAL<br/>if not using Minio]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|supported UI| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL]
    DSPO -->|custom CAs| TrustedCA[ODH Trusted CA Bundle<br/>INTERNAL]
    DSPO -.->|optional mTLS| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>INTERNAL<br/>Optional for MLMD]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|API calls| DSPO
    Elyra[Elyra] -->|pipeline authoring| DSPO
    SDKs[kfp-tekton SDK] -->|programmatic| DSPO

    %% Platform Services
    DSPO -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>PLATFORM]
    DSPO -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[Service CA Operator<br/>PLATFORM]
    DSPO -->|auth| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>PLATFORM]

    %% Tekton to Storage
    Tekton -->|artifact storage| Minio[Minio<br/>Default Storage]
    Tekton -.->|artifact storage| ExtS3

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

